OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784827121
OL,3,CPriest faces 116 child sex offence
OL,4,Ccharges
OL,6,FA priest is facing trial charged with
OL,7,F116 child sex offences.
OL,9,FEdward Gallagher (59) formerly of
OL,10,FOrchard Park in Lifford, County
OL,11,FDonegal but with an address at
OL,12,FMaghaberry Prison appeared for a
OL,13,Fpreliminary enquiry hearing at
OL,14,FLondonderry Magistrate's Court on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,17,FHe faced a total of 116 charges that
OL,18,Fwere said to have occurred on dates
OL,19,Fbetween June 22 2023 and April 18 2025.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
