OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784827121
OL,3,CPriest faces 116 child sex offence
OL,4,Ccharges
OL,6,FThey include among others sexual
OL,7,Fcommunication with children, attempted
OL,8,Fsexual communication with children,
OL,9,Fpossessing indecent images of children
OL,10,Fand inciting children under 16 to
OL,11,Fengage in sexual activity.
OL,13,FDefence solicitor Derwin Harvey told
OL,14,Fthe court he had gone through the
OL,15,Fcharges with Gallagher and there was
OL,16,Fno need for all 116 to be read out in
OL,17,Fcourt.
OL,19,FIt was accepted there was a case to
OL,20,Fanswer and there were no contrary
OL,21,Fsubmissions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
