OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784827121
OL,3,CPriest faces 116 child sex offence
OL,4,Ccharges
OL,6,FGallagher said he did not want to call
OL,7,Fany witnesses or make any statement at
OL,8,Fthis stage.
OL,10,FHe was returned for trial to the Crown
OL,11,FCourt on a date to be fixed and
OL,12,Fremains in custody.
